&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Commercial &amp;amp; Strategic Acumen&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience defining professional services offerings, engagement models, and pricing strategies&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
