&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Track record navigating complex enterprise sales cycles, particularly with Fortune 500 accounts&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Skill in cross-functional leadership: you&#39;ve aligned Sales, Product, Engineering, and CS organizations around common goals&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
